entry.title: Solar LED Flood Light - 20 Watt - 2000 Lumens - 4000K - 150W MH Equal
entry.summary:
Vendor: Light Efficient Design
Type: Solar Powered LED Lights
Price: 469.50

Solar LED Flood Light - 20 Watt - 2000 Lumens - 4000K - 150W MH Equal

 

The Solera solar flood light fixture features an all-in-one design. The solar panel and battery are built into the LED fixture. No need for a power source, which eliminates the need for trenching or wiring. Perfect for signage, billboards, walls, pathways and garden features. This fixture will turn on at night automatically, staying at 100% power for 4 hours and then dimming down to 25% for the rest of the night.


  • 4 hours of 100% brightness, then 25% for the remainder of the night
  • Adjustable LED flood light to point light where needed
  • Battery life up to 50 hours
  • Battery charge time takes about 8-9 hours
  • 50,000 hour LED life rate
  • 120° Beam angle
  • 3 year warranty
  • 20W Fixture comparable to a 150W HID
  • All-in-on design, solar panel and battery are built into LED fixture
  • Battery can support 5-6 nights with cloudy days.
